headline: Nordson EFD Takes Assembly Automation to Center Stage at MD&M West, February 3 – 5, 2026
summary: EAST PROVIDENCE, R.I., January 20, 2026--Nordson EFD will take Assembly Automation to center stage at MD&M West, February 3-5, 2026 for medical device assembly manufacturers in Anaheim, CA.
